OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day across
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland and Scotland, with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of showery rain which could
OL,8,Fbe heavy at times. Breezy around
OL,9,Fwestern coasts here. Dry across
OL,10,FEngland and Wales with plenty of warm
OL,11,Fspells of sunshine and light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FFurther showery outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain will move across the north and
OL,15,Fwest of the UK, but it will remain
OL,16,Flargely dry in the southeast with
OL,17,Fclear spells. Mild for all.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
