OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA fresher feeling day, with a
OL,6,Fmixture of sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, Showers most frequent in the
OL,8,Fnorth. Feeling pleasant in the sunnier
OL,9,Fmoments, especially in the south.
